GameState (enum):
SHOWING_MENU
PLAYING
SHOWING_GAMEOVER
Game:
game.setState(gameState = SHOWING_MENU):
if (activeGameState == gameState) return
if (activeGameState not null):
activeGameState.removeFromCanvas()
activeGameState = gameState
activeGameState.addToCanvas()
